rows.label: qst700901_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, you! Yeah, you.
I hear you've been busy, right?
People've been talking.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0002
rows.name:
You helped my kid brother the
other day, too. As a citizen of this
great town, I salute you. Thanks!

rows.label: qst700901_msg0003
rows.name:
So, uh, on that note... I've got a bit of a
request myself. Would that be all right?
It's been on my mind lately...

rows.label: qst700901_msg0004
rows.name:
You see, it's started appearing in those
woods there. ...And don't ask me what
"it" is, or anything stupid like that, OK?

rows.label: qst700901_msg0005
rows.name:
You don't believe me, do you? I didn't
either, 'till I saw it with my own two
eyes... Could you, uh, take a look?

rows.label: qst700901_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm in charge of this spot here so
I can't very well leave my post...
Can I count on you?

rows.label: qst700901_msg0007
rows.name:
If you just check the woods' entrance,
you'll be able to pick up some hints.
I'm sure someone was there!

rows.label: qst700901_msg0101
rows.name:
I'm sure someone was at the entrance
to the woods. It'd be great if you could
look for some kind of...trace.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0102
rows.name:
I'm the only one here now, right?
So I can't leave my post...
Sorry to drop this on you so suddenly.

rows.label: qst700901_msg0103
rows.name:
But I just can't stop thinking about it!
I just need to put my mind at ease.
Please go look before it's too late!
